Heydecke G(1), Penrod JR, Takanashi Y, Lund JP, Feine JS, Thomason JM.

Author information:
(1)Faculty of Dentistry, McGill University, 3640 University Street, M73, 
Montreal, Quebec H3A 2B2, Canada.

Implementation of new therapies is usually governed by financial considerations, 
so efficacy studies should also include cost comparisons. The cost and 
effectiveness of mandibular conventional dentures (CD, n = 30) and two-implant 
